---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE, t } from '../../../data/i18n.js';
const lang = 'en';
---
<Base lang={lang} title="Guided Tour of Ávila — Book with María Victoria Solaz" description="Dramatized guided tour of Ávila. UNESCO walls, Saint Teresa. Certified Heritage guide." path="/avila/guided-tour/">
  <div class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 overflow-hidden">
    <img src="/img/avila/muralla-atardecer.webp" alt="Walls of Ávila" class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="626" height="417" loading="eager" />
  </div>

  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Guided Tour</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-sepia mb-8">Ávila — UNESCO World Heritage</p>
    <section class="mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Duration</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">Flexible</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Price</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">On request</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Languages</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">EN · ES · IT · FR · PT</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>A dramatized tour through the Ávila that doesn't appear in conventional guides. Medieval walls, Saint Teresa's convent, the fortress-cathedral.</p>
        <p>For those who want to understand Ávila beyond the walls. Combines with El Escorial and Segovia.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="cta-green rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Book your tour</h2>
      <p class="text-sepia mb-4">Contact María Victoria directly</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/34659953930?text=Hello%20María%20Victoria%2C%20I'd%20like%20a%20guided%20tour%20of%20Ávila" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block btn-whatsapp px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium">💬 WhatsApp</a>
      <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70 mt-4">Usually replies within 24 hours</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
